mayo_lng_tlk_info_page1									= "So what do you want to know about?"
mayo_lng_tlk_weekly_page1								= "Why not read some weekly Percy Propa magazines?\nThis might help you struggle less."
mayo_lng_tlk_weekly_page2								= "Unfortunately, Mayo doesn't have all the issues."
mayo_lng_tlk_weekly_page3								= "Many issues have been lost during the war of the fallen."
mayo_lng_tlk_mayo_page1									= "Ahh so you want to know more about this procurer of rare\nresources huh? Getting to know the competition is that it?"
mayo_lng_tlk_service_page1								= "So what do you want?"
mayo_lng_tlk_service_page2								= "Ehh! So you want more?"
mayo_lng_tlk_service_page3								= "What more do you want huh?"
mayo_lng_tlk_item_page1									= "These are the available resources that Mayo can spare\nat the moment."
mayo_lng_tlk_item_page2									= "So you want key items? How about some Ice Cream\nor a So-Chlo perhaps?"
mayo_lng_tlk_item_page3									= "Or recruit personnels to slave on your facilities?"
mayo_lng_tlk_weapon_page1								= "Simply put, some of the weapons Mayo acquired from the\nbattlefield or was given to her. Others she have stolen\nfrom the main facility of this <#pt> Panopticon."
mayo_lng_tlk_weapon_npc_page1							= "Some of the weapons have been customized to suit the\nprevious owner's combat style and may not work. Read\nthe <#color_blue>Percy Propa Weekly<#color_def> for details."
mayo_lng_tlk_weapon_npc_melee_page1						= "Mayo have a variety of custom melee weapons used only\nby the best <#player>s."
mayo_lng_tlk_weapon_npc_melee_page2						= "Just be warned, not all of these weapons will work as\nintended."
mayo_lng_tlk_weapon_npc_melee_page3						= "Some are prototypes and not fully tested on the battlefield.\nThe weapons are also heavily modified, specially made to\nfit the previous owner's combat style."
mayo_lng_tlk_weapon_npc_pistol_page1					= "Mayo have a variety of custom pistols used only by the\nbest <#player>s."
mayo_lng_tlk_weapon_npc_pistol_page2					= "Just be warned, not all of these weapons will work as\nintended."
mayo_lng_tlk_weapon_npc_pistol_page3					= "Some are prototypes and not fully tested on the battlefield.\nThe weapons are also heavily modified, specially made to\nfit the previous owner's combat style."
mayo_lng_tlk_combat_page1								= "Mayo intercepted and acquired a couple of trucks full of\ncombat item crates. Ammo, grenades and some medical\nsupplies, Percy Propa dolls you name it."
mayo_lng_tlk_combat_munition_page1						= "Mayo have a full cache of munitions stored on her\nCell Garden hideout so don't hold back."
mayo_lng_tlk_combat_munition_page2						= "Have you tried the BENKEI? They are good for ambushing\nblind <#player>s and dumb Accessories."
mayo_lng_tlk_combat_medical_page1						= "Mayo have a full cache of medical supplies stored on\nher Cell Garden hideout so don't hold back."
mayo_lng_tlk_combat_medical_page2						= "...Or hold back and Mayo will have a new Will'O\nAlternator to sell."
mayo_lng_tlk_combat_medical_page3						= "...Or a brand new Accessory. Like yours."
mayo_lng_tlk_augment_page1								= "If you feel like you're dragging your feet then use augments."
mayo_lng_tlk_augment_page2								= "Mayo recommends Anti-Howl. This augment enables\nyou to attack while the abductor is busy wasting\nits time howling."
mayo_lng_tlk_augment_page3								= "Thorn Master is a good augment. It enables you to launch\nyour thorn while attacking. Good for quick escapes."
mayo_lng_tlk_resource_page1								= "By exploiting Mayo's position at the OPS Department\nshe has acquired a comfortable supplies of resources\nthanks to our valued <#player>s."
mayo_lng_tlk_resource_page2								= "And a couple boxes of Percy Propa dolls."
mayo_lng_tlk_key_page1									= "You want the rare stuffs? How about some Ice Cream?\nMayo have them all even the ones you haven't heard\nof."
mayo_lng_tlk_key_note_page1								= "So Julien needs you to fetch something?"
mayo_lng_tlk_key_note_page2								= "No sweat, Mayo got the resources here. Like Mayo have\nsaid, she got everything even the ones you haven't\nheard of."
mayo_lng_tlk_citizen_page1								= "Have you met Mayo's personnels? Aren't they loyal and\nsmall? They are well fed and love working with her. She\ncan spare you some of her trusted personnels if you want."
mayo_lng_tlk_citizen_page2								= "Didn't you know that when a Citizen is demoted to a\n<#player> status their body will undergo a modification. In\nshort they gain height and their body become stronger."
mayo_lng_tlk_shackle_page1								= "This feature is not permanent so feel free to get weird."
mayo_lng_tlk_music_bgm_page1							= "Rare record tracks left behind by a primitive civilization\nduring the pre-Panopticon era."
mayo_lng_tlk_music_bgm_page2							= "The record will be played here at the <#color_blue>Warren Hub<#color_def>,\nusing the PM system salvaged from the Shawshank\nPanopticon."
mayo_lng_tlk_music_bgm_page3							= "If they do catch you messing with the hub's PM system,\nyou don't know Mayo okay."
